## 5. Rendering Integration

### Plan View — `src/renderers/SvgCanvas.jsx`
- Import `usePhaseFilteredFloor`
- After `const floor = getFloor(activeFloorId)` (line 71), compute:
  ```js
  const filteredFloor = usePhaseFilteredFloor(floor, project, activePhaseId, phaseViewMode);
  ```
- Pass `filteredFloor` to all renderers (lines 348-364) instead of `floor`
- Keep `floor` (unfiltered) for `SelectionOverlay` and tool previews so selection/interaction still works on all objects
